Overview

Demonstrates successful execution of a qualified borrower through the complete HyperSync Lender Operating System.

Shows operational movement through:

Lender Intake OS
→ Lender Process OS
→ Lender Outbound OS
→ Lender System OS

with successful governance updates, loan officer assignment, and final completion.

Recording Objectives

Demonstrate:

Borrower intake

Loan type tagging

Validation pass

Routing decision

CRM synchronization

Loan officer assignment

Audit logging

Final completion
